# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files
**

# Re-include directories first so files inside them can be re-included below.
# Without this, `**` excludes the directories themselves and Docker cannot descend
# into e.g. cmd/ to pick up cmd/main.go (behavior varies by Docker/BuildKit version).
!**/

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!go.mod
!go.sum
